gFameCheckerFlavorText_Agatha4::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The inner circle?\p"
	.string "{FONT_FEMALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}I hear OAK’s taken an interest in\n"
	.string "your progress, child.\p"
	.string "That old man used to be a proper\n"
	.string "heavyweight and a looker.\p"
	.string "But that was decades ago.\n"
	.string "He’s just a shadow of his old self.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Agatha5::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What’s her vibe?\p"
	.string "{FONT_FEMALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}Look at AGATHA, for real.\p"
	.string "She set the record for the oldest\n"
	.string "ever member of the ELITE FOUR.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Lance0::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What's his hustle?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}I’m the leader of the ELITE FOUR.\p"
	.string "You can call me LANCE, the\n"
	.string "DRAGON master.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Lance1::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The preferred squad?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}You know dragons are mythical\n"
	.string "POKéMON.\p"
	.string "Hard to catch, hard to raise, but\n"
	.string "their power levels are unmatched.\p"
	.string "They’re basically indestructible.\n"
	.string "You can't outsmart 'em.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Lance2::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What’s his vibe?\p"
	.string "{FONT_FEMALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}He stands for justice!\n"
	.string "He’s cool and passionate!\l"
	.string "LANCE is the absolute GOAT!$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Lance3::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The word on the street…\p"
	.string "{FONT_FEMALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}LANCE is a regular customer of ours.\p"
	.string "He’s always buying new capes.\p"
	.string "I wonder… does he have a wardrobe\n"
	.string "full of the exact same cape?$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Lance4::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The inner circle?\p"
	.string "{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}LANCE’s grandad is basically the\n"
	.string "elder of a legendary clan of\l"
	.string "dragon masters.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Lance5::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The inner circle?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}Word is, LANCE has a cousin who’s\n"
	.string "a GYM LEADER way out in another\l"
	.string "region.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Bill0::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What's his hustle?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}BILL is world-famous as a total\n"
	.string "POKéMANIAC. A real enthusiast.\p"
	.string "He even built the POKéMON Storage\n"
	.string "System on the PC. Proper tech.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Bill1::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The preferred squad?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}BILL’s got a madness of POKéMON!\n"
	.string "He collects all the rare ones too!$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Bill2::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What’s his vibe?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}That’s my grandson!\p"
	.string "He was always out here collecting\n"
	.string "things, even when he was a tot!$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Bill3::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The preferred squad?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}BILL is a POKéMANIAC, so he rates\n"
	.string "every single type.\p"
	.string "Word is, the first one he ever\n"
	.string "caught was an ABRA. Safe choice.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Bill4::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The inner circle?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}BILL’s hometown is GOLDENROD,\n"
	.string "where his folks are still posted.\p"
	.string "I heard it’s a proper lively city,\n"
	.string "bare festive vibes everywhere.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Bill5::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The word on the street…\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}Apparently, BILL can’t even handle\n"
	.string "a drop of milk. Weak stomach, fam.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_MrFuji0::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What's his hustle?\p"
	.string "{FONT_FEMALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}He’s a real one.\p"
	.string "He looks after all the abandoned\n"
	.string "and orphaned POKéMON.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_MrFuji1::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What’s his vibe?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}This old guy stepped right up to\n"
	.string "our HIDEOUT, no fear.\p"
	.string "Started ranting about how TEAM\n"
	.string "ROCKET is moving foul.\p"
	.string "So, we’re just 'negotiating' with\n"
	.string "the elder right now.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_MrFuji2::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What’s his vibe?\p"
	.string "{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}POKéMON FAN MAGAZINE\n"
	.string "Monthly Grand Prize Drawing!\p"
	.string "The application form is…\p"
	.string "Gone! Clipped out. Someone already\n"
	.string "tried to secure the bag.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_MrFuji3::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The word on the street…\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}I hear MR. FUJI isn’t originally\n"
	.string "from these ends, you know?$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_MrFuji4::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The inner circle?\p"
	.string "{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}It’s a photo of BLAINE and\n"
	.string "MR. FUJI.\p"
	.string "They’re standing shoulder to\n"
	.string "shoulder, grinning like legends.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_MrFuji5::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What’s his vibe?\p"
	.string "{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}Editor: The shy MR. FUJI ducked\n"
	.string "our interview requests.\p"
	.string "He’s a kind soul who’s bare\n"
	.string "respected in LAVENDER TOWN.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Giovanni0::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What's his hustle?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}TEAM ROCKET takes POKéMON from\n"
	.string "all over the globe.\p"
	.string "They’re vital assets for keeping\n"
	.string "the business booming.\p"
	.string "I’m the boss, GIOVANNI!$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Giovanni1::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The preferred squad?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}Those goons that raided the spot…\p"
	.string "Their BOSS said he was only\n"
	.string "looking for high-tier POKéMON.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Giovanni2::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What’s his vibe?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}TEAM ROCKET’s BOSS is moving\n"
	.string "bare cold-hearted!\p"
	.string "To him, POKéMON are just tools\n"
	.string "to help the come-up.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Giovanni3::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What's his hustle?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}Welcome to my hideout!\p"
	.string "It stays like this until I get\n"
	.string "TEAM ROCKET back to the top.$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Giovanni4::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}What's his hustle?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}I’m shook! GIOVANNI was actually\n"
	.string "the LEADER of VIRIDIAN GYM?$"

gFameCheckerFlavorText_Giovanni5::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}The inner circle?\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}Wait… you’re not GIOVANNI’s son,\n"
	.string "are you?\p"
	.string "Nah, can’t be. The boss’s kid\n"
	.string "has red hair. Bare different.$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_ProfOak::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}PROF. OAK$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_ProfOak::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: PROF. OAK\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}Why do POKéMON go so hard for you\n"
	.string "in every battle?\p"
	.string "It’s because they see the real\n"
	.string "trust you’ve got for them.\p"
	.string "Don't ever let that slide.$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Daisy::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}DAISY$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Daisy::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: DAISY\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_FEMALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}While I was chilling and having\n"
	.string "my tea, you’ve become a legend.\p"
	.string "Keep being a proper rival to my\n"
	.string "little brother, yeah?$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Brock::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}BROCK$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Brock::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: BROCK\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}The world is massive, so there’s\n"
	.string "bound to be bare tough TRAINERS.\p"
	.string "Let’s keep grinding so we can\n"
	.string "both stay on top!$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Misty::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}MISTY$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Misty::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: MISTY\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_FEMALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}I’m gonna keep putting in work\n"
	.string "here at the GYM.\p"
	.string "Once I’ve leveled up, I’m tryna\n"
	.string "hit the road and see the world.$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_LtSurge::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}LT. SURGE$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_LtSurge::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: LT. SURGE\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}Yo, kid!\n"
	.string "You proper shocked me in our match!\p"
	.string "I didn't think rookies had guts\n"
	.string "like yours.\p"
	.string "You’ve officially changed my mind\n"
	.string "about you! Safe!$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Erika::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}ERIKA$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Erika::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: ERIKA\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_FEMALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}I’m so happy that there are elite\n"
	.string "TRAINERS like you out there.\p"
	.string "Seeing you work motivates me to\n"
	.string "stop being lazy.\p"
	.string "Come link me again sometime.\n"
	.string "Zzz…$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Koga::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}KOGA$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Koga::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: KOGA\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}You and I have to keep our heads\n"
	.string "up and handle our business.\p"
	.string "Now, I’ve got to go train my\n"
	.string "daughter. Stay sharp.$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Sabrina::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}SABRINA$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Sabrina::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: SABRINA\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_FEMALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}The bond you have with your\n"
	.string "team…\p"
	.string "It’s a power that my psychic\n"
	.string "abilities could never touch.$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Blaine::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}BLAINE$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Blaine::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: BLAINE\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}My FIRE squad!\n"
	.string "They’re gonna be even more tech!\p"
	.string "Quick quiz: How many types of\n"
	.string "FIRE POKéMON exist? Get guessing!$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Lorelei::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}LORELEI$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Lorelei::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: LORELEI\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_FEMALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}I had to reach out and thank you\n"
	.string "for the assist.\p"
	.string "But don't get it twisted, that\n"
	.string "doesn't change our battles.\p"
	.string "Watch your back next time!$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Bruno::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}BRUNO$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Bruno::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: BRUNO\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}I’ve seen that high-tier power\n"
	.string "you and your squad carry.\p"
	.string "Next time, I might have to show\n"
	.string "you how to level up your own\l"
	.string "physical game!$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Agatha::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}AGATHA$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Agatha::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: AGATHA\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_FEMALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}When you get older, don't you\n"
	.string "dare go soft like that old duff OAK!\p"
	.string "Stay like me and keep the energy\n"
	.string "for the battle!$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Lance::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}LANCE$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Lance::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: LANCE\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}I’m thinking of heading back to\n"
	.string "the ends for a bit.\p"
	.string "I need to retrain my DRAGON squad\n"
	.string "and boost their levels.\p"
	.string "I’ll have to get you an invite to\n"
	.string "my hometown one day. Standard.$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Bill::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}BILL$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Bill::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: BILL\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}Yo! CELIO was gassing you up,\n"
	.string "saying you're the GOAT.\p"
	.string "Hearing that makes me happy.\p"
	.string "When you catch some rare mons,\n"
	.string "come show me the levels. Trust!$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_MrFuji::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}MR. FUJI$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_MrFuji::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: MR. FUJI\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}Instead of just looking out for\n"
	.string "the vibes of your own squad…\p"
	.string "…Can you make sure every POKéMON\n"
	.string "out there is living their best life?$"

gFameCheckerPersonName_Giovanni::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}GIOVANNI$"

gFameCheckerPersonQuote_Giovanni::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}{SHADOW LIGHT_BLUE}From: GIOVANNI\n"
	.string "To: {PLAYER}\p"
	.string "{FONT_MALE}{COLOR DARK_GRAY}{SHADOW LIGHT_GRAY}I’ve got absolutely nothing to\n"
	.string "say to you.\p"
	.string "I’m moving in silence and focusing\n"
	.string "on my own grind. Nobody else.$"

