PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureBrock::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose: PEWTER GYM\n"
	.string "LEADER BROCK!\p"
	.string "BROCK rarely cracks a smile, but\n"
	.string "word is, if he starts laughing,\l"
	.string "he’s got no chill and won't stop.$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureMisty::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose: CERULEAN GYM\n"
	.string "LEADER MISTY!\p"
	.string "Rumor has it MISTY lowkey stans\n"
	.string "LORELEI of the ELITE FOUR.$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureLtSurge::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose: VERMILION GYM\n"
	.string "LEADER LT. SURGE!\p"
	.string "LT. SURGE was reportedly a pilot\n"
	.string "back in the States.\p"
	.string "He used juice generated by\n"
	.string "POKéMON to power his jet.$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureErika::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose: CELADON GYM\n"
	.string "LEADER ERIKA!\p"
	.string "Word on the street is if you peak\n"
	.string "into the GYM, you'll catch ERIKA\l"
	.string "caught in 4K just snoozing.$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureKoga::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose: FUCHSIA GYM\n"
	.string "LEADER KOGA!\p"
	.string "KOGA is said to be an absolute\n"
	.string "expert on medicine.\p"
	.string "He even whips up custom remedies\n"
	.string "to get his squad back to 100.$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureSabrina::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose: SAFFRON GYM\n"
	.string "LEADER SABRINA!\p"
	.string "People say SABRINA is telepathic\n"
	.string "and links with her squad in\l"
	.string "battle without saying a word.$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureBlaine::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose: CINNABAR GYM\n"
	.string "LEADER BLAINE!\p"
	.string "BLAINE only takes the shades off\n"
	.string "when he’s in the lab cooking up\l"
	.string "new quiz questions.$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureLorelei::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose:\n"
	.string "ELITE FOUR's LORELEI!\p"
	.string "Famous for her calculated and\n"
	.string "icy battle style, LORELEI has\l"
	.string "a secret that’ll shake the fans!$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureBruno::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose:\n"
	.string "ELITE FOUR's BRUNO!\p"
	.string "BRUNO joined the ELITE FOUR because\n"
	.string "he’s thirsty to battle the top-\l"
	.string "tier TRAINERS in the game.$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureAgatha::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose:\n"
	.string "ELITE FOUR's AGATHA!\p"
	.string "Back in the day, AGATHA and PROF.\n"
	.string "OAK were rivals constantly beefing\l"
	.string "over who was the top TRAINER.$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureLance::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose:\n"
	.string "ELITE FOUR's LANCE!\p"
	.string "LANCE's grandfather is thought to\n"
	.string "be the OG of a legendary clan of\l"
	.string "dragon masters.$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureProfOak::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose: PROF. OAK,\n"
	.string "the POKéMON Researcher!\p"
	.string "The PROF reportedly stays with his\n"
	.string "grandkids DAISY and {RIVAL}.$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureDaisyOak::
	.string "This is a POKéMON JOURNAL from\n"
	.string "years ago…\p"
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\n"
	.string "CONTEST Special!\p"
	.string "The Spring POKéMON CONTEST's\n"
	.string "Grand Champion is DAISY OAK of\l"
	.string "PALLET TOWN! Legend!$"

PokemonJournal_Text_SpecialFeatureMrFuji::
	.string "POKéMON JOURNAL\p"
	.string "Expose:\n"
	.string "MR. FUJI of POKéMON HOUSE!\p"
	.string "Editor: The shy MR. FUJI ducked\n"
	.string "our interview requests again.\p"
	.string "He’s a real one who’s bare\n"
	.string "respected in LAVENDER TOWN.$"

